==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[off-line]]

===Etymology===
[[off]] + [[line]]

===Adjective===
'''offline'''

#Describes a system which is, at the moment, not connected (generally electrically) to a larger network.
#:a. Describes a [[generator]] or [[power plant]] which is not connected to the [[grid]].
#:b. Describes a [[computer]] which is not connected to the [[Internet]] or to any other [[communications]] service.
#::''I printed the web pages so I could read them later when I was '''offline'''.''

